description:
Watch Whirl Season 1 Ada and Friends: Volume 15 on Vision Video 

Episode 1: Disciple Requirements
Episode 2: Scary Charity
Episode 3: Anxieties Aweigh
Episode 4: Bias and Birdies 
Episode 5: All Sown Up
Episode 6: Baptism Barrage 
Episode 7: Grace Basket
Episode 8: Let My Monty Go!

Whirl is a Bible-based cartoon series about the lovable and sometimes overly-enthusiastic kids of First-Second Church. In each episode the kids tackle a different theme that is central to Christian values.  And while the issues dealt with are relatable, the solutions these kooky characters find are mostly…unconventional.  Kids of all ages will be laughing while they’re learning!

Whirl is a Bible-based cartoon series about the lovable kids of First-Second Church who tackle different themes that are central to Christian values.

Director: Jared Neher
Writer: Aaron Christopher, Nick Ryan, Matt Spring
Producer: Jared Neher, Aaron Christopher
Cast: Suzie Juul, Dave Gangler, Taj Ruler
